+-- ============================================================================
+-- FXL Sales integration — referral attribution columns
+--
+-- Adds nullable columns used by the FXL Sales affiliate integration:
+--   checkout_attempts.click_id  — FXL Sales click ULID (last-touch), threaded
+--                                 from ?ref at checkout time.
+--   checkout_attempts.fxl_sig   — raw ?fxl_sig referral HMAC. STORED ONLY;
+--                                 verification deferred per FXL Sales D-P.
+--   org_attribution.click_id    — propagated from checkout_attempts at the time
+--                                 first_paid_at is set, so the outbound conversion
+--                                 webhook can resolve attribution by click_id.
+--
+-- All columns are nullable (no backfill). Idempotent: IF NOT EXISTS guards.
+-- Forward-only.
+-- ============================================================================
+
+BEGIN;
+
